---
layout: base
title: Blog - ReferVo
description: Tips, guides, and insights on growing your business through referrals. Learn how contractors, realtors, and service professionals can earn more with ReferVo.
---

<div class="blog-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>ReferVo <span>Blog</span></h1>
    <p>Tips, guides, and insights on growing your business through referrals</p>
  </div>
</div>

<section class="blog-section">
  <div class="container">
    {# Category Filter #}
    <div class="blog-categories">
      <a href="/blog/" class="category-pill active">All</a>
      <a href="/blog/category/contractors/" class="category-pill">Contractors</a>
      <a href="/blog/category/realtors/" class="category-pill">Realtors</a>
      <a href="/blog/category/agencies/" class="category-pill">Agencies</a>
      <a href="/blog/category/tips/" class="category-pill">Tips</a>
      <a href="/blog/category/news/" class="category-pill">News</a>
    </div>

    {# Articles Grid #}
    <div class="articles-grid">
      {% for article in collections.articles %}
        {% include "partials/article-card.njk" %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>

    {% if collections.articles.length == 0 %}
    <div class="blog-empty">
      <p>No articles yet. Check back soon!</p>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  </div>
</section>

